.SH NAME
pstr-delete - Permanently delete messages from the local store


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpstr delete [id...] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Delete removes messages from the local Postero store permanently. Use trash if you need a reversible mailbox action.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for delete

.PP
\fB--stdin-ids\fP[=false]
	read message IDs from stdin as whitespace-separated values


